‼️CALL FOR ARTISTS & PERFORMERS‼️
RAGE! RAGE! RAGE! the art & pole show brought to you by kat savage @106fever and @maddy_frechette of @sirenchicago invite all former and current $3xw0rk3r artists and performers to apply. Society has overlooked and disrespected feminine rage, demonizing a perfectly valid reaction to oppression. Here, we will not allow society to diffuse our anger and frustration. Rage is powerful, that’s why the patriarchy has tried to suppress it for centuries. So we’re going to bare our teeth, channel this anger, and turn it into something sacred. so welcome, to RAGE! RAGE! RAGE! However you express, feel, and cope with this rage: we want to see it. We encourage you to lean into it; be primal, be feral, be ugly because WE FEEL YOU.

We are looking for current/former $exw0rk3rs who are also artists of any kind (2D and 3D), as well as performers (pole, floor work, burlesque). We encourage all participating artists to apply to the performance category as well, though it’s not required. 

❤️‍🔥HOW TO APPLY❤️‍🔥
For artists: send in artist name, bio, up to 3 pieces of work, Instagram handle, working titles and a bit about your piece and what RAGE! means to you to sirenx106fever@gmail.com with the subject title “RAGE ART” by December 15th. 

For performers: send in performer name, bio, concept/description of what your performance will be, song title you’d like to perform to, video/link of you performing, and Instagram handle to sirenx106fever@gmail.com with the subject title “RAGE PERFORMANCE” (or ‘RAGE BOTH’ to submit for both categories). The video submission doesn’t have to be your final piece, but give us an idea of your style for this performance. We want unapologetic intensity and expression.

Exact location is TBD but will be announced in December. The show is January 14, 2023. 

📸: @106fever
